WEBVTT

00:02.519 --> 00:03.520
[ Remote clicks ]

00:03.555 --> 00:05.074
[ Upbeat music plays ]

00:07.835 --> 00:10.527
♪ I don't care what you say!

00:12.253 --> 00:14.221
♪ I'm gonna do what I want
all day! ♪

00:14.255 --> 00:16.637
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:16.671 --> 00:18.570
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:18.604 --> 00:23.161
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:25.439 --> 00:29.581
♪♪

00:29.615 --> 00:32.756
[ Bell tolls ]

00:32.791 --> 00:35.587
[ Triumphant music plays ]

00:35.621 --> 00:41.248
♪♪

00:41.282 --> 00:46.287
♪♪

00:46.322 --> 00:49.221
I will call you Carla.
Mwah!

00:49.256 --> 00:54.399
♪♪

00:54.433 --> 00:59.576
♪♪

00:59.611 --> 01:02.614
[ Engine whirs ]

01:02.648 --> 01:05.789
[ Crowd cheering ]

01:05.824 --> 01:07.481
[ Crowd gasps, music fades ]

01:07.515 --> 01:09.138
Nice.

01:09.172 --> 01:10.449
[ Upbeat music plays ]

01:10.484 --> 01:12.486
[ Chuckling ]

01:12.520 --> 01:16.421
[ Making "vroom" noises ]

01:16.455 --> 01:18.457
[ Laughing ]

01:18.492 --> 01:19.596
There ya go!

01:19.631 --> 01:21.771
Oh! Ah, all right.

01:21.805 --> 01:24.498
[ Giggling ]

01:24.532 --> 01:26.603
[ Sighs ]

01:26.638 --> 01:29.848
Yeah, Carla, we have fun.

01:32.575 --> 01:34.439
What is that?

01:34.473 --> 01:36.510
Carla.

01:36.544 --> 01:38.615
Does it fly?

01:38.650 --> 01:40.824
[ "I don't know" shrug ]

01:40.859 --> 01:43.310
So lame.
Let's go, Mother.

01:45.208 --> 01:48.142
You know what --
I always drive.

01:48.177 --> 01:49.523
It's so selfish.

01:49.557 --> 01:51.663
Why don't you pick where we go,
Carla?

01:51.697 --> 01:54.252
This time...
you drive.

01:55.667 --> 01:59.498
[ Wind howls ]

01:59.533 --> 02:02.329
[ Gasps ]
Oh, my goodness, Carla!

02:02.363 --> 02:04.676
How are you doing this?
[ Chuckles ]

02:04.710 --> 02:06.678
Driving all by yourself!

02:06.712 --> 02:09.543
Oof. You sure we should
go in there, Carla?

02:09.577 --> 02:12.166
It looks pinchy.

02:14.513 --> 02:15.514
Okay!

02:15.549 --> 02:17.206
[ Grunting ]

02:17.240 --> 02:18.552
Ow.

02:18.586 --> 02:20.174
Ow, ow.

02:20.209 --> 02:23.177
Oh, hey!
Carla, you found me comics!

02:23.212 --> 02:24.868
[ Chuckles ][ Video game noises ]

02:24.903 --> 02:26.836
You should drive
on all our adventures.

02:26.870 --> 02:28.493
Where to next, my Carla?

02:30.460 --> 02:31.703
[ Humming ]

02:31.737 --> 02:34.878
After rough riders, we meet
Mavis for an ice cream social.

02:34.913 --> 02:36.949
Oh, uh-huh.Then I made an appointment
to make lanyards with Darlie.

02:36.984 --> 02:38.675
Oh, yeah, yeah.She's got
a whole bucket of gimp,

02:38.710 --> 02:40.263
and I don't want to miss out
on the premium colors.

02:40.298 --> 02:42.886
-Yeah, I'm up for anything.
-Really?

02:42.921 --> 02:44.957
What if I told you
we were gonna go to,

02:44.992 --> 02:46.890
oh, I don't know,
to the dentist?

02:46.925 --> 02:48.789
You'd want to do that?
-No.

02:48.823 --> 02:51.447
But you agreed to do
anything on this itinerary.

02:51.481 --> 02:53.759
Is going to the dentist
on there?

02:53.794 --> 02:56.383
No, but--Cool.

02:56.417 --> 02:58.730
Uh, what are you drawing?

02:58.764 --> 02:59.903
I'm just winging it.

02:59.938 --> 03:01.767
[ Engine whirs ]Hey, guys!

03:01.802 --> 03:03.355
What happened to you?

03:03.390 --> 03:06.013
[ Chuckles ] Carla
was showin' me around town.

03:06.047 --> 03:07.428
She found these!

03:07.463 --> 03:09.879
Oh! Nice!

03:09.913 --> 03:11.743
What do you mean,
she's showing you around?

03:11.777 --> 03:13.469
You're still driving it
with the remote.

03:13.503 --> 03:15.574
I may be holding
the remote...

03:15.609 --> 03:18.888
[ Sniffles ]
...but Carla's driving.

03:18.922 --> 03:20.993
It's obvious you're the one
controlling the car.

03:21.028 --> 03:22.236
-There she goes again!
-Whoa!

03:22.271 --> 03:24.549
Come on, Jeff,
before you miss it!

03:24.583 --> 03:25.895
I'm gonna have to move
some things around.

03:25.929 --> 03:26.930
[ Upbeat music plays ]

03:26.965 --> 03:29.416
Come on![ Laughing ]

03:29.450 --> 03:35.801
♪♪

03:35.836 --> 03:38.287
Wow!
[ Laughs ]

03:42.532 --> 03:43.913
[ Panting ]

03:46.329 --> 03:48.297
[ Gasps ]
Ooh!

03:48.331 --> 03:52.646
-Oh!
-Whoa, oh!

03:52.680 --> 03:55.407
[ Music continues]

03:55.442 --> 04:03.795
♪♪

04:03.829 --> 04:05.900
Whoa!
Football.

04:05.935 --> 04:07.833
Whoa.
-Clock.

04:10.698 --> 04:14.357
Gosh, I'm sorry, Darlie!
Please stop yelling, Darlie.

04:14.392 --> 04:16.773
Clarence: Carla's so cool...
[ Chuckles ]

04:16.808 --> 04:20.432
Right?It's fun, but it's just leading
us to random places.

04:20.467 --> 04:22.710
But it's not too late
to get back on schedule.

04:22.745 --> 04:25.610
A quick chat with Darlie,
and then ice cream with Mavis!

04:25.644 --> 04:28.026
Uh-oh. Jeff!

04:28.060 --> 04:30.684
Guys, come on. Darlie's house
is in the opposite direction.

04:30.718 --> 04:32.858
Come on, Jeff,
follow that car!

04:32.893 --> 04:35.309
Wow, I didn't know
there was a path here.

04:37.484 --> 04:39.624
Hmm.
I wonder what it found.

04:39.658 --> 04:41.488
It's a hole.

04:41.522 --> 04:45.837
[ Gasps ] Oh, wow!
Carla found this!

04:45.871 --> 04:47.563
-Oh, Jeff!
-Aah!

04:47.597 --> 04:50.980
See, Jeff! Carla knows
where the good stuff is.

04:51.014 --> 04:52.464
That's trash
with worms in it!

04:52.499 --> 04:54.086
If we stick
to my schedule,

04:54.121 --> 04:55.812
we're guaranteed
to have a fine time.

04:55.847 --> 04:57.745
I do want to see Mavis.

04:57.780 --> 04:59.851
Can Carla come, too?

04:59.885 --> 05:02.336
Yes, Clarence,
you can bring your toy car.

05:02.371 --> 05:03.510
Now let's see,
we missed Breehn,

05:03.544 --> 05:05.408
so we can move him
to next week, and--

05:05.443 --> 05:08.515
Carla! Wha! Would you --
can you guys believe this?!

05:08.549 --> 05:09.343
Oh, my!

05:09.378 --> 05:12.346
Come on, man --
classic Clarence.

05:12.381 --> 05:14.969
Whoa, wait for me, Carla!
[ Grunts ]

05:15.004 --> 05:17.731
[ Laughing ]

05:17.765 --> 05:19.698
Whoa!

05:19.733 --> 05:23.495
[ Upbeat music playing ][ Beeping ]

05:25.773 --> 05:27.568
[ Screeching ]

05:27.603 --> 05:30.709
[ Squawking ]
Help! Help! Save me!

05:30.744 --> 05:34.679
Uh, Clarence,
did Carla mean to bring us here?

05:34.713 --> 05:35.714
[ Grunting ]

05:35.749 --> 05:37.923
[ Beeping ]

05:37.958 --> 05:39.511
Carla's not moving.

05:39.546 --> 05:42.480
-Just give her a moment...
-Clarence...

05:44.620 --> 05:47.485
[ Gasps ]
Wait, guys, um...

05:47.519 --> 05:50.729
Carla was leading us here --
to this old potato chip!

05:50.764 --> 05:53.629
-Yuck!
-Filthy.

05:53.663 --> 05:54.940
Praise Carla!

05:54.975 --> 05:56.735
This is just typical.

05:56.770 --> 05:58.047
I have to reschedule with Darlie
for the fifth time today.

05:58.081 --> 05:59.635
Of course.

05:59.669 --> 06:00.739
Hello, operator?

06:00.774 --> 06:01.775
I'm hungry!

06:01.809 --> 06:05.917
Oh, um, I'm pretty sure
Carla wants to eat, too.

06:05.951 --> 06:08.126
♪♪

06:08.160 --> 06:10.749
See?
I told you Carla was hungry!

06:10.784 --> 06:12.613
Ugh!

06:12.648 --> 06:14.650
[ Cries ]

06:14.684 --> 06:16.721
Feed me, Carla!

06:16.755 --> 06:23.659
♪♪

06:23.693 --> 06:26.420
[ Groans ]Clarence, let's go.

06:26.455 --> 06:28.802
Mm-hmm, yep!
She's almost done!

06:28.836 --> 06:30.424
Gah! Enough!

06:30.459 --> 06:32.081
Following this car around
just led us

06:32.115 --> 06:33.116
to an afternoon
of crumminess!

06:33.151 --> 06:34.911
[ Gasps ] Jeffery!

06:34.946 --> 06:36.982
I had all these ideas
for activities for today,

06:37.017 --> 06:38.950
but we can still
get ice cream with Mavis.

06:38.984 --> 06:42.505
But -- but Carla
is my best friend I ever had --

06:42.540 --> 06:45.094
who has the bestest ideas
all the time.

06:45.128 --> 06:46.647
Clarence,
Carla is not real.

06:46.682 --> 06:51.203
Oh, yeah?
Then who made that drawing?

06:51.238 --> 06:53.861
Ow. You!
You're the one controlling it!

06:53.896 --> 06:57.140
Here, look! I can draw the same
picture, let me just...

06:57.175 --> 07:00.661
[ Beeping ]Wait, what the heck
is going on?

07:00.696 --> 07:03.940
♪♪

07:03.975 --> 07:06.149
What?

07:06.184 --> 07:09.187
Jeff, I said -- right!

07:09.221 --> 07:12.708
[ Tires squeal ]Whoa, she's going crazy!

07:12.742 --> 07:13.985
Whoa!

07:14.019 --> 07:15.952
Okay, I'm interested.

07:15.987 --> 07:17.678
[ Barking ]

07:17.713 --> 07:19.473
Jeff: Can this really
be happening?

07:19.508 --> 07:21.613
She probably
just short-circuited.

07:21.648 --> 07:23.132
Oh, I'm telling you,
guys,

07:23.166 --> 07:25.755
Carla's gonna show us
something real special.

07:25.790 --> 07:27.205
All: Whoa!

07:27.239 --> 07:29.690
-Carla, wait!
-Whoa!

07:29.725 --> 07:32.555
-Sumo, come on!
-That's a really steep hill.

07:35.627 --> 07:39.666
Plus, I still want to hang out
with Mavis, right, Jeff?

07:39.700 --> 07:42.496
I kind of want to see
where Carla goes.

07:43.877 --> 07:46.120
Hmm...
we'll never catch her now.

07:46.155 --> 07:47.294
[ Grunts ]

07:47.328 --> 07:48.744
Give me that.
What the?!

07:48.778 --> 07:50.021
Oh, hey!

07:50.055 --> 07:51.885
Were you thinking about
going down this hill?

07:51.919 --> 07:54.163
Yeah.
Oh, extreme!

07:54.197 --> 07:56.855
Well, you're definitely
going to be needing this.

07:56.890 --> 07:58.098
And these.

07:58.132 --> 08:00.065
Nice knowing ya!Thanks, Rita!

08:00.100 --> 08:01.757
Are you guys
out of your minds?

08:01.791 --> 08:04.587
Going down that hill --
in the middle of the street?!

08:04.622 --> 08:06.244
Do you know
how dangerous that is?!

08:06.278 --> 08:08.211
In or out, Sumo?Yeah!

08:08.246 --> 08:11.249
I am out!

08:11.283 --> 08:13.009
-Ready?
-Ready!

08:13.044 --> 08:16.081
[ Screaming ]

08:16.116 --> 08:18.601
Hmm.
I think I want to go...

08:18.636 --> 08:21.017
Oh, heavy traffic!
Scary!

08:21.052 --> 08:23.675
[ Screaming ]

08:23.710 --> 08:26.747
Can you help me across?

08:26.782 --> 08:31.062
[ Screaming ]

08:31.096 --> 08:33.029
Isn't this so much fun?

08:33.064 --> 08:34.893
[ Screaming ]

08:34.928 --> 08:37.171
[ Grunts ]

08:37.206 --> 08:39.553
[ Chuckling ]

08:39.588 --> 08:40.727
Whoa!

08:40.761 --> 08:41.900
[ Crash! ]

08:41.935 --> 08:44.247
-Yay!
-Aah!

08:44.282 --> 08:47.906
-Here! Take one of these!
-No!

08:47.941 --> 08:49.908
[ Screaming ]

08:49.943 --> 08:52.911
Whoa!

08:52.946 --> 08:54.913
Mmm, mmm, mmm.

08:54.948 --> 08:56.812
[ Screaming ]

08:56.846 --> 08:59.573
[ Gasps ] I'm alive!Carla! Carla! Carla!

08:59.608 --> 09:02.058
[ Grunting ]Carla! Carla!

09:02.093 --> 09:06.580
Carla! Carla! Carla!

09:06.615 --> 09:09.272
You're going to be okay.

09:09.307 --> 09:12.862
Why did you bring us here?!
Why did you bring us here?!

09:12.897 --> 09:14.968
There must be a reason
you brought us to this place!

09:15.002 --> 09:18.765
Um, maybe it's about the journey
and not the destination.

09:18.799 --> 09:23.770
She was in the trash bag!
Check the trash!

09:23.804 --> 09:25.737
[ Gasps ]

09:25.772 --> 09:27.601
Smokin'!

09:27.636 --> 09:31.812
Carla nails it again.
[ Chuckles ]

09:31.847 --> 09:34.608
No! Carla!

09:37.266 --> 09:40.787
[ Beeping ]

09:40.821 --> 09:42.927
Ugh, finally!
Geez, what even was that?

09:42.961 --> 09:45.757
Why was it glitching out
all day long until just now?

09:45.792 --> 09:47.932
Sumo, Sumo -- why can't --

09:47.966 --> 09:50.279
why'd you --
why'd you do that?!

09:50.313 --> 09:51.798
She was my dearest friend!

09:51.832 --> 09:54.283
She led us here
for a reason!

09:54.317 --> 09:56.768
Murderer!

09:56.803 --> 09:59.150
Now now,
let's not call names.

09:59.184 --> 10:00.427
Just give me the bat

10:00.461 --> 10:02.118
and we can try to fix Carla.

10:02.153 --> 10:04.017
Look at yourselves.

10:04.051 --> 10:07.676
You've been digging through
trash, you're covered in dirt!

10:07.710 --> 10:09.160
You could've been killed
coming down that hill!

10:09.194 --> 10:12.784
The Carla thing was fun at
first, but this is just stupid!

10:12.819 --> 10:15.131
Okay, man,
just -- just hear me out...

10:15.166 --> 10:18.307
And we did none of the stuff
on Jeff's list!

10:18.341 --> 10:19.998
[ Grunts ]

10:20.033 --> 10:22.000
[ Panting ]

10:22.035 --> 10:24.796
I really wanted to eat ice cream
with Mavis.

10:24.831 --> 10:26.660
I haven't seen Mavis
in forever!

10:26.695 --> 10:28.006
-Hmm.
-Mm.

10:28.041 --> 10:31.838
So, what do you have to say
for yourselves?

10:31.872 --> 10:33.943
-Sorry, Sumo.
-Sorry, Sumo.

10:33.978 --> 10:36.014
Hmm.

10:36.049 --> 10:42.020
[ Soft music plays ]

10:42.055 --> 10:45.955
I suppose this is what Carla
was always traveling towards...

10:45.990 --> 10:47.370
her grave.

10:47.405 --> 10:48.924
You're doing the right thing,
man.

10:48.958 --> 10:52.755
Sleep now and forever,
my Carla.

10:52.790 --> 10:55.862
You'll be someone else's
buried treasure now.

10:55.896 --> 10:59.348
[ Slurping ]

10:59.382 --> 11:02.006
So, Mavis,
how have you been?

11:02.040 --> 11:03.663
[ Laughter ]

11:04.491 --> 11:06.320
♪ Early to bed

11:08.081 --> 11:09.945
♪ Early to rise

11:11.360 --> 11:13.396
♪ Picking my nose
